item.title: closed note (near Máriapócs) / * 2020 September 17 14:31 bkil Resolved: Hello, / We welcome any map error reports that you submit using the OpenStreetMap “Map Notes” function. / Note that what you write here is public and this function is not meant to be used for private notetaking. Please refer to: https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/Notes / I recommend you check out this service built on top of OSM where you can create your own layers and labels on top and even share it with your friends: / https://wiki.openstreetmap.org/wiki/uMap / Best regards
